# Harness Health

Use this checklist during PR review, release prep, or a monthly maintenance pass.

- [ ] `AGENTS.md` still matches the current repo layout and commands.
- [ ] `scripts/agent-check.sh` or equivalent still runs successfully.
- [ ] CI covers the important local checks.
- [ ] Approved fixtures or golden examples still represent real business behavior.
- [ ] Safety rules cover secrets, logs, destructive commands, deployments, migrations, and production data.
- [ ] Dependency and secret-scan results have been reviewed.
- [ ] Recent repeated review comments have been converted into docs, checks, or fixtures.
